            "title": "盤中速報 - 昇陽半導體(8028)股價殺至跌停，跌停價148.5元，成交16,260張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昇陽半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8028:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8028\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8028-TW</a>)08日10:21下跌16元，股價跌停報148.5元，委買2,590張、委賣294張，成交16,260張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為晶圓再生及晶圓薄化代工服務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>昇陽半導體(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8028:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8028\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8028-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲28.52%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.96%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+20,603 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+19,127 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+1,447 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+29 張</li> <li>融資增減：+339 張</li> <li>融券增減：+1,618 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
